## Map + Fold + Guard

Sketch that maps a list, filters the results, and folds them:

```scheme
;; SKETCH (four steps)
(define raw '(1 2 3 4 5))
(define squared (map (lambda (n) (* n n)) raw))
(define evens (filter (lambda (n) (= (modulo n 2) 0)) squared))
(fold + 0 evens)
```

Collapse:

```scheme
;; ONE SHOT
(fold + 0 
      (filter (lambda (n) (= (modulo n 2) 0)) 
              (map (lambda (n) (* n n)) 
                   '(1 2 3 4 5))))
```

The map closes inside the filter, the filter closes inside the fold. One form. No `squared`. No `evens`.

