(define medium (cond (has-voice \"speech\") (has-screen \"text\") (else \"log\")))
medium
```

Collapse:

```scheme
;; ONE SHOT
(cond ((system/registry :domain \"voice\") \"speech\") 
      ((system/registry :domain \"display\") \"text\") 
      (else \"log\"))
```

*[needs: system/registry]*  
